These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, jazz, trance
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, mauve, white, light-blue
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, climbing, handball
 1. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 6. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the fan of blues##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
13. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | country | jazz    | blues   |
| Color   | blue | white | mauve | light-blue |
| Pet           | dog       | horse   | rabbit  | cat     |
| Sport     | baseball      | climbing   | handball    | basketball    |

