.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
City: rome, paris, london, miami
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, thriller, time-travel
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, collecting, gardening, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5
 7. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
 8. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| City          | rome   | london       | miami    | paris      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | crime         | thriller   |
| Hobby   | fishing   | puzzles  | collecting       | gardening |
| Sport         | golf      | volleyball  | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

