.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, designer, project-manager, social-worker
There 4 different types of food: apricot, cranberry, lemon, cauliflower
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, russian, spanish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, water, 7up
 1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the bartender and the person eating lemon##7
 3. the designer is the polish##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 6. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person eating apricot##5
 7. the project-manager is not the person eating cranberry##6
 8. the person eating lemon is not the social-worker##6
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
11. the designer is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
12. the russian is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Job           | social-worker | bartender | designer | project-manager |
| Food   | apricot        | cauliflower    | cranberry    | lemon    |
| Nationality   | german        | spanish   | polish   | russian         |
| Beverage           | cola          | milk       | 7up   | water           |

