 7. the nurse is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching thriller movies##7
 8. the journalist is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the japanese##3
10. the doctor is the italian##1
11. the tiparillo-smoker is between the baccarat-smoker and the journalist##2
12. the scientist is the blend-smoker##1

