 5. the havana-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
 6. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is not the owner of the dog##6
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
12. the owner of the snake is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
13. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the owner of the turtle##7
