.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat, swisher, ritmeester
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, lemon, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, hiking, reading
House: cape-cod, art-deco, palace, futuristic
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 2. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the futuristic house and the palace house##2
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the art-deco house##6
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the person eating pear##7
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 9. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the siglo-smoker is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the palace house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar   | baccarat   | ritmeester     | swisher   | siglo |
| Food       | pear   | apricot | artichoke | lemon    |
| Hobby      | hiking | reading | dancing   | drawing  |
| House        | futuristic | cape-cod     | palace   | art-deco |

