.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, october, april
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, chess, filmmaking
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, designer, police-officer, writer
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, canasta, bridge
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 2. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's hobby is chess and the architect##2
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person playing billiard is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 8. the person playing monopoly is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 9. the writer is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
13. the police-officer is on the left of the writer##1
14. the architect is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
15. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Birthday      | march      | september        | april          | october    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping    | chess          | board-games |
| Job           | architect  | designer   | police-officer | writer      |
| Game   | bridge       | monopoly | canasta          | billiard        |

