.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different games are played: whist, poker, bridge, snooker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, metal, pop, blues
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the fan of pop is the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the person playing snooker and the person playing poker##2
 5. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the fan of pop and the person playing whist##7
 7. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the fan of metal##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of trance##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game   | snooker      | bridge     | poker   | whist    |
| Music-Genre     | blues | pop   | metal | trance |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 